%N A396793 G.f. A(x) satisfies A(x) * A(A(x)) = x^2 + 9*x^3.
%C A396793 Conjecture: a(n) == 0 (mod 3) for n > 1.
%H A396793 Paul D. Hanna, <a href="/A396793/b396793.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..401</a>
%F A396793 G.f. A(x) = Sum_{n>=1} a(n)*x^n satisfies the following formulas.
%F A396793 (1) A(x) * A(A(x)) = x^2 + 9*x^3.
%F A396793 (2) x * A(x) = R(x)^2 + 9*R(x)^3 where R(A(x)) = x.
%F A396793 (3) A(A(A(x))) = A(x)^3/x^2 * (1 + 9*A(x))/(1 + 9*x).
%e A396793 G.f.: A(x) = x + 3*x^2 - 12*x^3 + 81*x^4 - 645*x^5 + 5367*x^6 - 43092*x^7 + 302817*x^8 - 1441422*x^9 - 3502845*x^10 + ...
%e A396793 RELATED SERIES.
%e A396793 The second iteration of A(x) begins
%e A396793 A(A(x)) = x + 6*x^2 - 6*x^3 + 9*x^4 + 60*x^5 - 1083*x^6 + 10260*x^7 - 54894*x^8 - 268110*x^9 + 12650094*x^10 + ...
%e A396793 where A(x) * A(A(x)) = x^2 + 9*x^3.
%e A396793 The third iteration of A(x) begins
%e A396793 A(A(A(x))) = x + 9*x^2 + 18*x^3 - 54*x^4 + 117*x^5 + 954*x^6 - 18792*x^7 + 187821*x^8 - 1182006*x^9 + 1703916*x^10 + ...
%e A396793 where A(A(A(x))) = A(x)^3/x^2 * (1 + 9*A(x))/(1 + 9*x).
%o A396793 (PARI) {a(n) = my(V=[0,1,3],A); for(i=1,n, V=concat(V,0); A=Ser(V);
%o A396793 V[#V] = -polcoef(A * subst(A,x,A), #V)/3; ); polcoef(GF=A,n)}
%o A396793 {upto(n) = a(n); Vec(GF)}
%o A396793 upto(25)
